headline: Pace selected by Prudential Financial to help automate its insurance operations with agentic AI
summary: NEW YORK, December 04, 2025--Pace, the agentic workforce for insurance, was chosen by Prudential’s Individual Life Insurance (ILI) business to help simplify and improve its service delivery.
